Great Job!  Now we need a web server

Lets install our web server `beefy` that 
will do all kinds of neat things for us, 
like calling browserify everytime their 
is a change to our source files, and even 
live reload in the browser!

FYI, the --save flag automatically adds
the module to our package.json dependencies
list.

Cow Says:  npm install beefy --save && ./n
